<i>noun</i>: 잔디 [잔디] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>잔디 [잔디]</dt><br>
<dd>turf; sod; grass</dd><br>
<dd>정원, 공원, 골프장 등에 심는 잎이 짧고 가늘며, 촘촘하게 자라는 풀.</dd><br>
<dd>Grass that have short, narrow leaves, grow close together, and are planted in a garden, park, golf links, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>